assets.description: Created in the space environment on top of the moon (wish we could see this on the web), MoonSat One: "Most of the world's AI processin' gets done there cost-free -- with satellite photovoltaics and whatnot -- then beamed back to Earth. The mining and tourism deltas rake it in surface-side... In the biosphere, yeah, it's just like home -- better, in fact, cleaner! It's perfect... But up there? That's God's house. It's Mount Olympus. Who knows what's goin' on up there. It ain't no reason for us to go up anymore, it's so automatic. And no one's lining up to, I'll tell ya. I wonder if they... if they like it here, I guess? Do they like what they do for us? Do they care? I do wonder."

assets.description:
So Rave is my Sonic OC (has been for about 6 years now) and one of his defining features is a orange-flame emblazoned robotic arm. He's gone through several revisions but I think the current design is definitely the best (created by my friend sharlet). this design features a zero-gravity hand, suspended in the air with separated digits. This is a (very) low poly model depicting it's basic features. ^^

Worked on the shoulder pad up top a bit. Closer to where I want it.
